title: D3 Supp/Top LFT/Dynamic Friends.
body:
Hey guys, 
basically just looking for some people to play with around mid/high diamond with. 
Not really fussed, just don't be super toxic and be high spirited. 
Simply looking to play with a group or so of people who understand the game and looking to improve in a better environment. 
 IGN   - Stev (D5)
          - Facta non Verba (D3)
Stev is my main and general account I used to practice/have fun on so idk add both if you're keen.
Cheer :)
